social_posts.post_text: Stumbled upon Christmas magic in Easton, PA yesterday. The most adorable small town vibes - felt like I was dropped into a Hallmark movie set. Antique shops, holiday music, Santa, yummy treats and even real reindeer. Add this to your Christmas cheer travel list. #christmastown #hallmarkmovies #eastonpa

Visions of sugarplums should be dancing in my head but ghosts of Christmas past pop up instead… 

#christmasdecorations #christmastable #christmasmemories

Santa stopped by our little corner of Brooklyn today! It’s a good thing too because with just 2 weeks to go, this Christmas season is flying by! Many thanks to Abby and her elves for making it happen!

Visited the Titanic Exhibit today with Aggie. I was hoping for a more interactive experience (really loved recreated hallway!) This was more of an audio tour with some interesting artifacts to see behind glass but we enjoyed it anyway.  Always something new to do here! #titanicexhibition #titanic #thingstodoinnyc #thingstodowithkidsinnyc

Lap catting 

#catsofinstagram #scottishfoldtabby #greykitten #christmascatsofinstagram
Merry Christmas wishes from 1979. That chair is boho style goals! I can almost feel the wicker. Hope your holidays are more cozy than my brother and I are in this snapshot.
Lucky for me, he does all the cooking! Merry Christmas fellow gift wrappers!

Christmas Mail call! As you know, we send out a little surprise with our Christmas cards every year. This year we gave our our favorite sweets: chocolate truffles! The 4 of us are obsessed with these - hoping our friends and family enjoy them just as much as we do. 

#christmascards #newyearscard #chocolatetruffles #sweetnewyear #catsonchristmascards #christmasmail #grandmillennial #catsfirstchristmas

Meatball got her deluxe apartment in the sky! 

#scottishfold #cathomedecor #bougiecat #catcondo #santapaws #meatballthecat #catpeople

I’m living the parable about slow and steady winning the race over here at our beach renovation. Still not done but the awful brick mural (yes, the “bricks” you see on the wall were just painted rectangles on drywall. Very kr8tiv. 🥺) has been updated. Floating shelves + base cabinet doors to be added. Should I paint the brick hearth the same beige I’m using on the wall paneling or do all white? 

#fireplacemakeover #fireplacebuiltins #chantillylace #babyfawn #slowrenovation #beachhouse #coastalstyle #wallmolding

Not my usual content but I had to share this fun find. A little time travel back to my 80s childhood! The best part is you pay one price and can play it all.

#familyfun #xennialmom #childofthe80s #jerseyshore #90minsfromnyc #retroarcade

2022 had too many happy memories to fit into one fast recap but I tried anyway. In my typical tradition we took our new year snap early and hope to sleep through midnight. Happy New Year to all of you! May 2023 grant all of your wildest wishes!

Rather than making a list of all the ways I fall short (aka resolutions), I’m making a mental note of all the joyful moments I had in the last year. As I get older I’m reminded that each year finished is one less left to live - but can be revisited in my mind and in my camera roll as long as I’m here. That will do.

This spot is so hard to photograph but I’m overjoyed to have this new fixture finally hung. Perfect mix of transitional / coastal style without being too on the nose. (Link in profile) Such a huge improvement from the before! Now what kind of artwork should I hang in here?

Well, it’s official. The kitty we thought was a Polpetta (Italian word for Meatball) actually has his own meatballs! Jokes on us. No matter! We love him just as much as if he was a she. Enjoy your swagger for a little longer kitty. Your pre-neuter days are coming to an end soon.
#meatballthecat #catsofnyc #britishshorthair #scottishfold #catpeople #genderreveal #catfamily

It wouldn’t be Christmas without our annual #christmasmail tradition where we send out a little gift along with our greetings. This card is also a testament to the fact I never got around to getting a family photo taken #momfail but thankfully Meatball stepped in as our substitute. Swipe to see! This year’s gift is a screw lock keychain to “ring” in the new year. Get it? “Ring”! Come on people, this is gold! Anyway, I starting using one of these keychains this year and is a far better mousetrap than the standard keychain. Trust me! You are welcome. 
#christmascard #stockingstuffers #catsofchristmas #christmascat #printdesign
The perfect photo does not exist. #meowychristmas

Help! This is our first Christmas we will be serving food buffet style instead of the usual sit down dinner service. I know some of you are super hostesses! Please give me all your tips on how to make this go smoothly but also feel fancy. Pretty please 🙏 

As I await your tips I will share 2 favorites featured in this photo. The first is this wood and glass floral holder that I stuffed with garland greens from @glassandwood_ .The second are these “kitchen towels” I found on Amazon that are cuter, better and less expensive than proper cloth napkins and can still be delivered before Christmas! 

Ok back to task at hand. Lay your advice on me!

#buffetstyle #entertainingtips #napkins #tablescape #holidayentertaining

Let’s normalize mom’s stocking being the fullest! 

#stockings #christmasdecor #livingroom #christmasinbrooklyn 🎄

Nothing makes me feel older than thinking about how fast time flies. Every year goes by faster than the last. I’m truly grateful for all of the love, luck and joy we have had in 2023. Let’s make 2024 even better! 

#yearinreview #nycfamily #familytravel #brooklynfamily

This is your reminder to take a similar photo of your family every year. We have been doing this since Oscar was born and it’s a special moment in time to look back on every year. The years really are short! Happy New Year everyone. 🥂

Ok I’m obsessed with this motion activated lighting situation. What a change ambient light makes in a dark hallway! Thanks to everyone who helped me figure out that I should stop looking for a motion activated lamp and just buy a plug in sensor! Duh! (If you want your own, it’s listed in my Amazon favorites in my profile.) Now onto figuring out a mirror or artwork to hang here. 

#lightinghacks #hallwaylighting #motionactivated #stairwelllighting #ambientlight #amazonfinds
